    "seo": {
      "title": "MRI Coccyx: Fast, Radiation-Free Imaging at Cadabams Diagnostics",
      "description": "Learn why an MRI coccyx scan is the safest way to diagnose tailbone pain. Cadabams Diagnostics offers 3T & open-MRI with same-day reports—book today.\n",
